29:39.720 --> 29:43.300
and next thing I know

29:43.300 --> 29:44.440
I see this shadow

29:44.440 --> 29:45.540
in the fog.

29:45.660 --> 29:46.160
I'm looking ahead

29:46.160 --> 29:47.080
and I see the shadow

29:47.080 --> 29:50.660
and I see a man,

29:51.020 --> 29:51.700
which would appear

29:51.700 --> 29:52.300
to be a man

29:52.300 --> 29:54.100
or a humanoid figure

29:54.100 --> 29:55.900
emerge from the fog.

29:56.080 --> 29:56.520
And I thought,

29:56.580 --> 29:57.100
well, what the heck?

29:57.200 --> 29:59.480
Did the sergeant walk back?

29:59.900 --> 30:03.060
And that's my first thing.

30:03.100 --> 30:04.180
Well, the sergeant walked back

30:04.180 --> 30:06.920
and I couldn't figure why.

30:06.920 --> 30:07.940
But then the next thing,

30:08.140 --> 30:09.960
this figure kept coming

30:09.960 --> 30:10.420
towards me.

30:10.460 --> 30:11.840
Now, it had like

30:11.840 --> 30:12.780
a trench coat on.

30:13.280 --> 30:13.720
Really?

30:13.860 --> 30:14.940
Very similar to

30:14.940 --> 30:16.500
the raincoats

30:16.500 --> 30:17.240
that were issued

30:17.240 --> 30:18.060
to the officers.

30:18.620 --> 30:20.420
And he had a cap on,

30:20.620 --> 30:22.000
which could have been.

30:22.180 --> 30:23.120
So my next thing,

30:23.320 --> 30:23.880
well, I wonder

30:23.880 --> 30:24.940
if there's some officer

30:24.940 --> 30:27.060
checking up on me.

30:27.160 --> 30:28.360
But as it got closer,

30:28.480 --> 30:29.860
I realized this was not

30:29.860 --> 30:31.120
what it was.

30:31.300 --> 30:33.240
And I could feel it

30:33.240 --> 30:35.160
in my mind.

30:35.280 --> 30:36.020
I mean, it was like

30:36.020 --> 30:37.880
it was, it started

30:37.880 --> 30:38.980
grabbing hold of me.

30:39.400 --> 30:40.620
And I became

30:40.620 --> 30:41.480
really frightened.

30:42.560 --> 30:44.200
And as it approached me,

30:44.320 --> 30:45.860
I tried to pull my pistol.

30:45.980 --> 30:47.000
We had 38 police

30:47.000 --> 30:49.080
as part of our gear.

30:49.120 --> 30:50.240
And I tried to pull my pistol

30:50.240 --> 30:51.500
and my right arm

30:51.500 --> 30:52.180
was paralyzed.

30:52.380 --> 30:53.240
I couldn't move it.

30:53.740 --> 30:54.960
I could move my body,

30:55.040 --> 30:56.220
but I couldn't move my arm.

30:56.620 --> 30:58.060
And I became more terrified.

30:58.900 --> 31:00.660
And it became closer to me.

31:00.660 --> 31:05.460
Something, I can't see the face

31:05.460 --> 31:06.460
in my brain.

31:06.540 --> 31:07.800
If I try to see this face,

31:07.840 --> 31:08.600
I can't see it.

31:08.640 --> 31:09.260
It's a blank.

31:09.900 --> 31:11.080
But whatever it was

31:11.080 --> 31:12.140
was terrifying me.

31:12.580 --> 31:13.880
And whatever it was

31:13.880 --> 31:14.880
had control of

31:14.880 --> 31:16.640
at least my right arm.

31:17.160 --> 31:18.120
And I was standing

31:18.120 --> 31:19.480
just outside the shack.

31:19.540 --> 31:21.200
And I backed into the shack

31:21.200 --> 31:24.440
just instinctively, I guess.

31:24.440 --> 31:27.380
And I got myself back

31:27.380 --> 31:28.580
to the back of the shack

31:28.580 --> 31:29.900
and there was nowhere

31:29.900 --> 31:30.680
else to go.

31:31.080 --> 31:32.640
And the figure was coming,

31:33.060 --> 31:34.640
continued coming towards me.

31:35.040 --> 31:36.440
And there was a shelf

31:36.440 --> 31:37.000
at the back.

31:37.100 --> 31:37.800
There was a telephone

31:37.800 --> 31:38.480
on there and it was

31:38.480 --> 31:39.120
just a shelf.

31:39.560 --> 31:40.360
And I can remember

31:40.360 --> 31:42.480
distinctly pushing my back

31:42.480 --> 31:43.760
into that shelf

31:43.760 --> 31:44.460
and trying to push

31:44.460 --> 31:45.540
the back of the shack out.

31:45.600 --> 31:47.000
I was like a rat

31:47.000 --> 31:48.160
caught in a trap.

31:48.640 --> 31:50.000
And the terror was just,

31:50.780 --> 31:52.420
I couldn't describe how,

31:52.740 --> 31:53.720
I was just terrified.

31:53.720 --> 31:54.900
The next thing I know,

31:54.960 --> 31:55.840
I'm out, you know.

31:55.940 --> 31:56.560
And I don't know

31:56.560 --> 31:57.500
if I passed out

31:57.500 --> 31:59.340
or it's just blank

31:59.340 --> 32:00.060
at that point.

32:01.140 --> 32:04.620
So then I come to

32:04.620 --> 32:07.040
and I'm inside this,

32:07.760 --> 32:09.260
it's a circular room.

32:09.700 --> 32:11.100
I'm not going to call it a craft

32:11.100 --> 32:11.940
because I didn't see it

32:11.940 --> 32:13.140
from the outside,

32:13.400 --> 32:14.920
but I'm in this circular room.

32:15.580 --> 32:17.420
And I'm on my knees

32:17.420 --> 32:19.400
and there's about a

32:19.400 --> 32:20.860
two and a half,

32:20.940 --> 32:22.080
three foot circle

32:22.080 --> 32:23.420
that's open.

32:23.720 --> 32:24.140
clear.

32:24.520 --> 32:25.540
You could see through it.

32:26.500 --> 32:27.520
And there's this figure

32:27.520 --> 32:29.680
on my right-hand side

32:29.680 --> 32:33.280
and it's communicating to me,

32:33.380 --> 32:34.280
don't look at me,

32:34.380 --> 32:35.340
don't look over here,

32:35.380 --> 32:36.720
just look through the circle.

32:38.480 --> 32:40.500
And, you know,

32:40.560 --> 32:41.200
it's weird

32:41.200 --> 32:42.380
because it's not words.

32:42.860 --> 32:44.000
You know what it wants.

32:44.140 --> 32:44.860
It's like he's,

32:45.560 --> 32:47.180
it's very definitely a command,

32:47.320 --> 32:48.580
but it's not in words,

32:48.580 --> 32:49.480
but you know what,

32:50.440 --> 32:50.780
you know,

32:50.820 --> 32:51.260
I don't know

32:51.260 --> 32:52.160
other people have

32:52.160 --> 32:52.800
this psychic

32:52.800 --> 32:55.660
thought process

32:55.660 --> 32:56.620
or anything like that.

32:56.660 --> 32:57.080
But one thing,

32:57.180 --> 32:58.400
it was not words.

32:58.500 --> 32:58.940
It was just,

32:59.020 --> 33:00.320
I knew I was not

33:00.320 --> 33:01.100
to look at them,

33:01.420 --> 33:01.560
you know,

33:01.560 --> 33:03.060
just look at this circle.

33:03.060 --> 33:06.880
So I'm looking at the circle

33:06.880 --> 33:08.080
and what you see initially

33:08.080 --> 33:09.740
is just this gray fog,

33:09.840 --> 33:10.300
basically.

33:11.200 --> 33:12.220
One of the things I noticed

33:12.220 --> 33:12.980
at the time

33:12.980 --> 33:14.520
is that I would expect

33:14.520 --> 33:15.320
a breeze

33:15.320 --> 33:16.240
or something cold

33:16.240 --> 33:17.100
to be coming through

33:17.100 --> 33:18.400
and it wasn't.

33:18.500 --> 33:19.260
It's like there was

33:19.260 --> 33:19.820
a barrier,

33:20.040 --> 33:21.280
but it wasn't like glass.

33:21.440 --> 33:22.960
It was just clear.

33:24.080 --> 33:24.840
And all of a sudden,

33:25.260 --> 33:27.500
this kind of clears away

33:27.500 --> 33:28.920
like clouds splitting

33:28.920 --> 33:30.580
and there's a post

33:30.580 --> 33:31.860
about 100 yards

33:31.860 --> 33:34.200
down the street

33:34.200 --> 33:35.040
on the opposite side

33:35.040 --> 33:35.460
of the room.

33:35.560 --> 33:37.760
Now, I'm on site D5

33:37.760 --> 33:41.640
and this is site D11,

33:41.980 --> 33:43.180
which is across the street

33:43.180 --> 33:43.640
down there.

33:43.800 --> 33:45.640
I'm familiar with the site.

33:45.740 --> 33:46.820
I don't know which one it was.

33:47.560 --> 33:48.800
It's easily identifiable

33:48.800 --> 33:50.000
by the side of the street

33:50.000 --> 33:51.000
and the orientation.

33:52.360 --> 33:54.540
And it's just getting light

33:54.540 --> 33:56.880
and I can see this truck

33:56.880 --> 33:58.260
pull up to the gate

33:58.260 --> 34:00.280
and it had,

34:00.800 --> 34:02.120
it was a flatbed truck,

34:02.240 --> 34:03.300
a long flatbed truck.

34:03.740 --> 34:05.580
It had a lot of long pipes on it

34:05.580 --> 34:08.120
and the guard was to the,

34:08.660 --> 34:11.460
came over to the right side

34:11.460 --> 34:12.040
of the truck

34:12.040 --> 34:14.800
and obviously was getting ID

34:14.800 --> 34:15.700
or checking whether

34:15.700 --> 34:16.660
it was driving,

34:16.660 --> 34:17.320
went over,

34:17.820 --> 34:18.500
opened the gate,

34:18.620 --> 34:19.440
let the truck in

34:19.440 --> 34:20.240
and then the clouds

34:20.240 --> 34:21.060
closed up.

34:22.960 --> 34:24.080
And so,

34:24.320 --> 34:25.280
I'm still looking

34:25.280 --> 34:26.080
through this hole

34:26.080 --> 34:27.020
and I'm still just,

34:27.200 --> 34:27.460
you know,

34:27.500 --> 34:28.600
just keep looking

34:28.600 --> 34:29.200
through the hole

34:29.200 --> 34:31.360
and I kind of raised

34:31.360 --> 34:32.940
my eyes to look around

34:32.940 --> 34:34.240
without looking over

34:34.240 --> 34:37.040
and there were the opposite me

34:37.040 --> 34:40.540
about six,

34:40.660 --> 34:41.560
ten feet away

34:41.560 --> 34:43.560
were these four figures

34:43.560 --> 34:44.920
sitting on a bench

34:44.920 --> 34:46.200
and I could see

34:46.200 --> 34:47.100
that the wall

34:47.100 --> 34:50.520
of the craft,

34:50.660 --> 34:51.920
I'll call it a craft now,

34:52.360 --> 34:53.780
I could see that the bench

34:53.780 --> 34:54.920
was just a continuation

34:54.920 --> 34:56.660
of the material

34:56.660 --> 34:57.960
of whatever the wall was

34:57.960 --> 35:00.000
and whatever lighting

35:00.000 --> 35:00.820
was in there,

35:01.280 --> 35:02.880
the figures were silhouetted

35:02.880 --> 35:04.480
like the light source

35:04.480 --> 35:05.220
that's behind

35:05.220 --> 35:06.560
or from the wall

35:06.560 --> 35:07.180
but very,

35:07.300 --> 35:09.240
very consistent.

35:09.540 --> 35:09.680
I mean,

35:09.720 --> 35:10.320
there wasn't like

35:10.320 --> 35:11.320
bright lights or anything.

35:12.120 --> 35:12.640
Effectively,

35:12.740 --> 35:13.900
the room was pretty dark

35:13.900 --> 35:15.440
so the figures

35:15.440 --> 35:16.520
seemed silhouetted.

35:17.500 --> 35:18.680
It appeared to me

35:18.680 --> 35:20.060
like a baby

35:20.060 --> 35:21.280
had a large head

35:21.280 --> 35:23.060
and smaller body

35:23.060 --> 35:24.140
disproportionate.

35:24.640 --> 35:26.480
The eyes were discernible

35:26.480 --> 35:27.540
because they were darker

35:27.540 --> 35:30.200
than the skin features

35:30.200 --> 35:30.960
or whatever.

35:31.780 --> 35:32.840
A lot of people say

35:32.840 --> 35:33.440
they were,

35:33.760 --> 35:34.020
you know,

35:34.120 --> 35:34.820
these creatures

35:34.820 --> 35:35.640
or creatures,

35:35.760 --> 35:36.000
beings,

35:36.120 --> 35:36.400
whatever,

35:36.900 --> 35:39.880
were some sort of suit

35:39.880 --> 35:40.800
or something like that.

35:40.800 --> 35:41.920
I couldn't really tell that.

35:42.340 --> 35:42.780
Basically,

35:42.920 --> 35:43.420
a silhouette

35:43.420 --> 35:45.520
with just slight features

35:45.520 --> 35:46.080
available

35:46.080 --> 35:48.360
and there were two

35:48.360 --> 35:49.160
on one side

35:49.160 --> 35:50.320
and two on the other side

35:50.320 --> 35:51.500
with a space in between

35:51.500 --> 35:52.540
that I took

35:52.540 --> 35:53.740
to be some sort of door

35:53.740 --> 35:54.680
out of this room

35:54.680 --> 35:55.820
or something like that

35:55.820 --> 35:59.000
and that's about it.

35:59.100 --> 35:59.260
I mean,

35:59.360 --> 36:00.620
that's next thing I know.

36:02.100 --> 36:04.400
I'm sitting on the,

36:04.480 --> 36:05.560
I'm laying on the floor

36:05.560 --> 36:06.440
of the guard shack.

36:07.520 --> 36:09.040
There's like a little porch

36:09.040 --> 36:10.320
right in front of the door

36:10.320 --> 36:11.080
to the guard shack

36:11.080 --> 36:12.440
and I'm laying with my feet

36:12.440 --> 36:13.940
off the porch

36:13.940 --> 36:14.680
on the ground

36:14.680 --> 36:17.100
and this being

36:17.100 --> 36:19.040
is sitting on the porch

36:19.040 --> 36:20.060
and has my head

36:20.060 --> 36:20.700
at its lap

36:20.700 --> 36:23.560
and it's saying to me,

36:24.060 --> 36:25.320
it's communicating again,

36:25.420 --> 36:26.300
it's communicating,

36:27.260 --> 36:28.920
I'm sorry,

36:29.100 --> 36:29.340
you know,

36:29.400 --> 36:30.860
we didn't mean to scare you.

36:31.000 --> 36:31.380
He says,

36:31.380 --> 36:37.300
we didn't mean to scare you,

36:37.380 --> 36:39.380
but we had to have access

36:39.380 --> 36:40.800
to the site.

36:42.180 --> 36:45.260
So we needed the intelligence

36:45.260 --> 36:46.560
is what I was gathering

36:46.560 --> 36:47.560
out of this form

36:47.560 --> 36:48.380
of communication

36:48.380 --> 36:49.220
that they were just,

36:49.480 --> 36:51.000
needed access to the site

36:51.000 --> 36:52.460
and I was in the way.

36:52.460 --> 36:54.820
And so,

36:55.820 --> 36:59.660
it really felt comfortable.

37:00.140 --> 37:00.160
Like,

37:00.460 --> 37:00.780
you know,

37:00.820 --> 37:01.440
I felt like,

37:01.620 --> 37:01.740
well,

37:01.760 --> 37:02.440
this is okay,

37:02.540 --> 37:03.600
he's not going to hurt me,

37:03.720 --> 37:03.980
you know.

37:04.820 --> 37:05.760
So I was fine,

37:05.860 --> 37:06.220
you know.

37:06.500 --> 37:06.900
But I kept,

37:07.200 --> 37:08.200
the other thing

37:08.200 --> 37:08.920
was keep my eyes

37:08.920 --> 37:09.820
tightly shut.

37:10.320 --> 37:11.560
It did not want me

37:11.560 --> 37:12.340
to look at it

37:12.340 --> 37:12.840
or see it.

37:13.000 --> 37:14.160
Keep your eyes shut,

37:14.320 --> 37:14.600
you know.

37:15.120 --> 37:17.140
And I apologize,

37:17.280 --> 37:17.700
I'm sorry

37:17.700 --> 37:19.280
that we scared you so much,

37:19.340 --> 37:21.500
but we needed to have access

37:21.500 --> 37:23.140
and you were in the way.

37:24.060 --> 37:24.780
And he says,

37:24.840 --> 37:24.960
no,

37:24.980 --> 37:25.760
I'm going to leave

37:25.760 --> 37:26.960
and I want you to

37:26.960 --> 37:29.360
just keep your eyes shut.

37:29.580 --> 37:29.720
Just,

37:30.060 --> 37:30.280
you know,

37:30.340 --> 37:31.460
don't get up,

37:31.540 --> 37:32.120
don't do anything,

37:32.240 --> 37:33.340
just stay there

37:33.340 --> 37:34.300
with your eyes shut.

37:34.860 --> 37:36.140
And he left.

37:36.700 --> 37:38.080
And I did just what he said.

37:38.160 --> 37:38.720
I laid there

37:38.720 --> 37:40.060
for maybe 15 minutes

37:40.060 --> 37:40.960
with my eyes shut.

37:41.800 --> 37:42.600
And I was glad

37:42.600 --> 37:43.200
to see him go,

37:43.280 --> 37:43.680
frankly.

37:44.600 --> 37:46.200
And then I finally

37:46.200 --> 37:47.100
got up

37:47.100 --> 37:48.640
and looked around.

37:49.340 --> 37:51.100
And the sun was just,

37:51.760 --> 37:53.200
it had come over the,

37:53.420 --> 37:54.960
there's a ridge of mountains

37:54.960 --> 37:56.340
behind the,

37:56.340 --> 37:58.480
what we call D sector,

37:58.660 --> 38:01.440
probably a quarter of a mile back.

38:01.580 --> 38:02.900
And the sun was coming up

38:02.900 --> 38:03.820
over that ridge.

38:04.420 --> 38:05.760
And if you look towards the ocean,

38:05.860 --> 38:06.800
you could see the light

38:06.800 --> 38:07.800
coming,

38:08.260 --> 38:08.420
you know,

38:08.440 --> 38:09.360
lighting up the ocean.

38:09.580 --> 38:11.660
It was kind of a beautiful sight.

38:12.680 --> 38:14.580
And I looked over

38:14.580 --> 38:15.880
to my right

38:15.880 --> 38:17.140
and there was a little chipmunk

38:17.140 --> 38:17.800
on the ground.

38:18.940 --> 38:20.100
And I have never,

38:20.320 --> 38:21.580
I just felt so much love

38:21.580 --> 38:22.660
for that little chipmunk,

38:22.780 --> 38:23.040
you know.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.260
I felt like

38:25.260 --> 38:26.380
I was joined

38:26.380 --> 38:27.200
with that chipmunk,

38:27.360 --> 38:27.520
you know,

38:27.520 --> 38:29.000
one living creature

38:29.000 --> 38:29.520
to another.

38:29.680 --> 38:30.520
And the little chipmunk

38:30.520 --> 38:31.580
kind of just looked back

38:31.580 --> 38:32.080
at me

38:32.080 --> 38:34.820
and kind of scurried away.

38:37.180 --> 38:38.780
About 20,

38:38.860 --> 38:39.920
30 minutes later,

38:40.780 --> 38:41.960
the time would be

38:41.960 --> 38:43.000
probably around

38:43.000 --> 38:43.960
6,

38:44.020 --> 38:45.020
37 o'clock,

38:45.880 --> 38:46.880
my relief came.

38:47.340 --> 38:47.540
Now,

38:48.020 --> 38:48.580
the missiles,

38:49.080 --> 38:51.460
50,

38:51.560 --> 38:52.200
60 yards

38:52.200 --> 38:53.560
off the main road,

38:53.640 --> 38:54.320
there's a little road

38:54.320 --> 38:55.140
that goes to the,

38:55.140 --> 38:56.140
to the missile site.

38:56.980 --> 38:57.460
And,

38:57.540 --> 38:58.120
you know,

38:58.120 --> 38:59.500
my relief came down,

38:59.580 --> 39:00.140
relieved me,

39:00.140 --> 39:00.620
and then I,

39:00.820 --> 39:01.840
they were all delivered

39:01.840 --> 39:02.820
by these Air Force

39:02.820 --> 39:04.900
blue pickup trucks,

39:04.980 --> 39:05.380
four-door

39:05.380 --> 39:06.700
pickup trucks,

39:06.760 --> 39:07.160
basically.

39:08.180 --> 39:08.560
And

39:08.560 --> 39:10.340
I could have gotten

39:10.340 --> 39:11.200
their four-door,

39:11.280 --> 39:12.880
or four-door seat

39:12.880 --> 39:13.320
in the back.

39:13.380 --> 39:14.320
I could have gotten inside,

39:14.640 --> 39:15.740
but I didn't want to.

39:16.440 --> 39:17.600
I got in back

39:17.600 --> 39:17.960
and I,

39:18.040 --> 39:19.080
I put my back

39:19.080 --> 39:20.400
to the cab of the truck

39:20.400 --> 39:21.640
and I pulled my feet up.

39:22.420 --> 39:23.300
And then they went

39:23.300 --> 39:23.840
and picked up

39:23.840 --> 39:24.720
the other guards.

39:25.180 --> 39:25.380
And,

39:25.440 --> 39:27.180
I was just real quiet

39:27.180 --> 39:28.000
and they were asking me

39:28.000 --> 39:28.580
what's wrong.

39:29.160 --> 39:29.300
And,

39:29.400 --> 39:29.600
you know,

39:30.340 --> 39:31.840
and I knew something

39:31.840 --> 39:32.380
had happened,

39:32.500 --> 39:34.020
but I couldn't quite

39:34.020 --> 39:35.960
put my finger on it.

